      <title>中国重申在信心脆弱的情况下需要稳定人民币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-reiterates-need-for-steady-yuan-amid-fragile-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国重申需要防止人民币单方面波动，因为美元复苏和风险情绪不佳给亚洲各国货币带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-reiterates-need-for-steady-yuan-amid-fragile-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
